{"tid":25850,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"上坂堇入選雜誌百大巨乳偶像！","createTime":"2016-12-06T11:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T03:41:33.000Z","uid":30256,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c4d9065451218db73246320d896ca06f31e1539","tid":25850,"uid":30256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:14:09.000Z","msg":"日本德間書店出版的娛樂八卦雜誌《周刊朝日藝能》的最新一期中，公佈了100位巨乳偶像排行榜，知名美女聲優上坂堇不但混入其中，而且還獲得了第67名。<br />\n<br />\n在這個百大巨乳偶像排行榜中，上榜的多是性感寫真女星。在上坂堇的介紹頁裡可以看到其他女星都以性感聞名，而上坂堇作為一個聲優，有種亂入的感覺。不僅如此她還取得了67名的成績，排名屬中等水平，看來這本雜誌對上坂堇巨乳的認可度還是非常高的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ifx8wocp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fifx8wocp&h=7b150952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://holland.pk/mjw7c2st\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmjw7c2st&d=ugRGr0K6dq0P6yXV8xHYtEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=56eaf783\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/mjw7c2st</a><br />\n<br />\n此外，2年前她不少心去《Concrete Revolutio 超人幻想》的活動時，發佈了twitter 相片，給眼利的玩家看到了驚人一幕！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/73l2fpgm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F73l2fpgm&h=0ad6b37f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://holland.pk/a84730vk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa84730vk&d=ugRGr0K6dq0P6yXV8xHYtEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=5525415b\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/a84730vk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://holland.pk/j5i4elqo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj5i4elqo&d=ugRGr0K6dq0P6yXV8xHYtEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=69a77186\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/j5i4elqo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.gameapps.hk/news/20179\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.gameapps.hk%2Fnews%2F20179&d=ugRGr0K6dq0P6yXV8xHYtEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=7da2ec91\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.gameapps.hk/news/20179</a>"},{"pid":"6bcd74081542647afe0d34b